snippet.title: Hometopia OFFICIAL TRAILER: Your Home in the Metaverse.
snippet.description:
Hometopia is a PC game where you can build, design, and renovate beautiful homes across five unique neighborhoods, or freely build dream houses and neighborhoods with friends online 🏡

 💻 Join our discord community and check our other social medias to keep in touch: 💻
⚬ Official Website: http://www.hometopia.me/
⚬ Discord: https://discord.gg/fBczChD 
⚬ Twitter : https://twitter.com/HometopiaGame
⚬ Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/HometopiaGame
⚬ TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@hometopia
⚬ Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/HometopiaGame
